    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A first-person arcade action game about a chihuahua in a spacesuit and rollerskates.</strong><br>Inspired by Unreal Tournament (DM-Morpheus) and Bomberman on the NES.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You jump, shoot grenades, blow things up, and hunt for corn. The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > double jumps and gravity trampolines;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  a grenade launcher and stationary turrets;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  explosive bombs you can throw right onto enemies;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a laser-blocking shield (you can’t shoot while it’s on);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  enemies bursting into pieces;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  secrets, ammo, and golden corn to collect.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 levels, different enemy types, and a final boss.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t about deep meaning — it’s about jumps, impact, and explosions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a dog in a spacesuit. That’s all you need to know.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/622e6a43e2fcb69fd2bcd1cd156b8e62.poster.avif?t=1757027575\" width=615 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/622e6a43e2fcb69fd2bcd1cd156b8e62.webm?t=1757027575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/1ca20f44e14595ae47cf6965332450a8.poster.avif?t=1757027575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/1ca20f44e14595ae47cf6965332450a8.webm?t=1757027575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/ef096e8a5ed8d81d4c9f90094c309145.poster.avif?t=1757027575\" width=615 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293700/extras/ef096e8a5ed8d81d4c9f90094c309145.webm?t=1757027575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
